@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jhrlac(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v2
    v2 = (v1 * v1)
    tmp = (tmp + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.38) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.25)))
    v2 = ((v2 / v0) - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.62) * (tmp + 0.21 * v0 + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.abs((v2 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.61)))
    v2 = (0.09 / v1)
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.46)) / ((v1 + 0.18 - tmp + 0.51) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
